Explain which policy rule would match a given tool invocation

Usage: explain [OPTIONS] <TOOL> [ARGS]...

Arguments:
  <TOOL>     Tool type: bash, read, write, edit, tool (or full tool name like Bash, Read, etc.)
  [ARGS]...  The command, file path, or noun to check (remaining args joined)

Options:
      --json  Output as JSON instead of human-readable text
  -h, --help  Print help
